@node "install" "Installation!"

                              ***Installation***

        1:  Move MultiRead.rexx to somwhere in your Pfiles: dir.
            (i.e. pfiles:bbs/)
        2:  Load BBs menu into a text editor.
        3:  Under 1; Maintenance menu,  change the command "RF, Read File"
            so that it reads "!!RF, Read File"  (Without the quotes, of 
            course)
            (IMPORTANT!!  Must be renamed to "!!RF" for remote use!)
        4:  At the end of 1; Maintenance menu add the comand

                RF     |{#0pfiles:bbs/Multiread.rexx}
                        ^         ^
                        ^      Be sure this is the path where you placed
                        ^           the file!
               CTRL Q, Of course!

        5:  Reload bbstext/menu & your set to go!
        6:  (OPTIONAL) Load the file MultiRead.rexx into your fav text
            editor.  edit the Line
                               path="CNet:"
            to whatever default path you want the requestor to use.
            **NOTE:  This path must end in a ":" or a "/" !!
@endnode

